-- Ace Promotes Maleno to President of U.S. Insurance Unit
-- B y   E l i z a b e t h   B u n n
-- 2013-03-06T20:12:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-06/ace-promotes-maleno-to-president-of-u-s-insurance-unit.html
Ace Ltd. (ACE) , the insurer with
operations in more than 50 nations, promoted Chris Maleno to
division president of Ace USA, the U.S.-based retail unit.  Maleno joined the company in 2007 as president of Ace USA
regional operations and brings more than 25 years of industry
experience to the role, Zurich-based Ace said in a statement
released today by Business Wire. He will report to John Lupica,
chairman of the North America insurance division.  To contact the reporter on this story:
